              Â¿Listo para llevar tu clÃ­nica<br />
              <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-white/80">a la cima?</span>
            </h2>

            <!-- Subtitle -->
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/80 mb-8 sm:mb-10 md:mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto cta-subtitle-entrance px-2" style="text-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);">
              Agenda tu <strong class="text-[#b4cfa6]">diagnÃ³stico gratuito de 30 minutos</strong> y descubrÃ­ el potencial real de tu clÃ­nica
            </p>

            <!-- CTAs -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-8 sm:mb-10 md:mb-12 cta-buttons-entrance px-2">
              <a
